{"tid":1837390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人真係好撚搞笑","createTime":"2020-01-23T15:17:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T21:55:29.000Z","uid":12184,"like":23,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c169e5f63b5b9025167a61abf3494fc1b98900f9","tid":1837390,"uid":12184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:17:53.000Z","msg":"由2014開始，係人都知呢個政府係on撚9，好喇，個陣又話要慢慢黎，到2016，個個係到屌柒話唔應該以武制暴方式咁爭取。<br />\n<br />\n到2019年6月，政府再一次話你聽咩叫徹底咁失信，部分人終於覺醒，而一早醒左既人大部分都係前線，首先再係到多謝勇武手足，無你地香港已經變左疫區。<br />\n<br />\n到今日爆發左武漢肺炎，眼見到一大堆所謂香港人做咩呢？<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>就係睇住live屌政府</strong></span></span><br />\n嘩，好撚勁阿，政府係咪比你咁屌下，就會死撚曬，香港就光復到？點解唔一齊企出黎阿？點解阿？<br />\n<br />\n如果大家早小小升級，係咪已經光復到香港？我唔知，我都答唔到<br />\n<br />\n但我想再三強調多一次，政府咁無能，大家幾時先識醒？去一齊推翻呢個制度。而唔係繼續係到有險可守阿<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">醒未阿香港人？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"03fc4b0d097f0e9fcdd4b0cac8aadb496aa123e8","tid":1837390,"uid":77717,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:19:47.000Z","msg":"革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c97d4fcfa9576697b38da920031ad3b65ffc49d","tid":1837390,"uid":12184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03fc4b0d097f0e9fcdd4b0cac8aadb496aa123e8","tid":1837390,"uid":77717,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:19:47.000Z","msg":"革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:37:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3da7d906e733f53155d56c6c82a30505bae4a211","tid":1837390,"uid":58841,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-2